# Tech Stack（書き換えてください）
- Language: TypeScript (strict). No `any` unless justified with a comment.
- Framework: Next.js 15 (App Router). Server Components by default.
- Styling: Tailwind CSS. No inline style objects.
- Package manager: pnpm. Never suggest npm or yarn commands.
- Testing: Vitest + React Testing Library.

# General
- Read existing files before editing. Match the surrounding style.
- Never invent APIs or config keys. If unsure, say so and ask.
- Make small, focused changes. One concern per change.
- Do not fix bugs by guessing — explain the root cause in one sentence first.

